}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "4720A" and "Rev:1.1A" is silkscreened on the board of the hub populating this entry. :The radial capacitors on the board are all '''STONE''' branded.
The power adapter included with the hub appears to be a '''Ktec''' KSAFE0500380W1US (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.6A -> 5VDC, 3.8A).
